        "qnum":  10,
        "question":  "Using empathy to convey understanding and noting the patient\u0027s strengths, along with exploring their ambivalence and conflicts about change is a part of which of the following techniques?",
        "choices":  [
                        "Acknowledgment of emotions",
                        "Minimizing patients\u0027 concerns",
                        "Motivational interviewing",
                        "Premature interpretation",
                        "Summarizing"
                    ],
